#)Declare Variables in PLAY level:
-----------------------------------

*)Variables declared at play level are accessible to all the tasks that are there in PLAY.


==)Example-1: 

- name: declare variable in PLAY level
  hosts: local
  connection: local 
  
  vars:
	NAME: Megham
	RELATION: Soul
	
  tasks:
  ansible.builtin.debug:
    msg: " You are my {{ NAME }} and {{ RELATION }} "
	
	
*)Understand: During the execution it will call the variables and print the message





  